@startuml Neighbor-Army_help-with-covid

actor User
participant "Next.js Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Firebase Auth" as Auth
participant "Firebase Functions" as Functions
participant "Onfleet API" as Onfleet
participant "Sendgrid API" as Sendgrid
participant "Google Maps API" as GoogleMaps
participant "Twilio API" as Twilio
database "Firebase Firestore" as Firestore

User -> Frontend: Access application
Frontend -> Auth: Authenticate user
Auth --> Frontend: Return auth token

alt Request Help
    User -> Frontend: Submit help request
    Frontend -> Functions: POST /api/tasks
    Functions -> Onfleet: Create task
    Onfleet --> Functions: Task created
    Functions -> Firestore: Store task details
    Firestore --> Functions: Confirmation
    Functions --> Frontend: Task created response
    Frontend --> User: Display confirmation
else Offer Help
    User -> Frontend: Submit volunteer form
    Frontend -> GoogleMaps: Autocomplete address
    GoogleMaps --> Frontend: Address suggestions
    Frontend -> Functions: POST /api/workers
    Functions -> Onfleet: Create worker
    Onfleet --> Functions: Worker created
    Functions -> Sendgrid: Add to mailing list
    Sendgrid --> Functions: Email added
    Functions -> Firestore: Store volunteer details
    Firestore --> Functions: Confirmation
    Functions --> Frontend: Volunteer registered response
    Frontend --> User: Display confirmation
end

User -> Frontend: Enter phone/zipcode
Frontend -> Functions: POST /api/verify
Functions -> Twilio: Verify phone/zipcode
Twilio --> Functions: Verification result
Functions --> Frontend: Verification response
Frontend --> User: Display verification result

@enduml